content: Looks like the great purge of 2022 claimed https://build.fhir.org/ig/argonautproject/scheduling/, or is it just out of maintenance? Is the latest repository at https://github.com/argonautproject/scheduling the latest version?

The published version is here: http://www.fhir.org/guides/argonaut/scheduling/ . I don't think there is much different between it and the CI build, because I don't recall any updates since publishing. That repo is correct.
It probably needs to be updated to work with the template based publisher to republish.
